==Talalit==
Ilul Hâssan Id basàid gh ighrm n [[tiznit]] ɣ usggas n 1967 gh iffus n [[Lmrruk|umrruk]]. Z ɣ mẓî nes sul ittut s uɣdjaj n ayt umarg. liɣ dars yan d mraw (11) n usggas, iskr tarabbut nes tamzwarut. Idîd d trabbut n Ayt matn yat tsffift ɣ usggas n 1985. 

Ghik lli s yuls Idbasàid i umarg n mnnaw ɣ ismghurn n uzawan amaziɣ zund Belàid d Umntag d Uctuk, as isrs Hâssan tirsal ns gh ubaraz n ayt umarg. 

almuggar ns d Ɛmmuri Mbark. yan ɣ isutar n umarg amaziɣ ikfa i Hâssan yat tarmi yadênin. Nttan ad d issar mnnaw iwiznn ɣ mnnawt tmizar n Urubba. Yaws as ɣ yat gh tsffifin ns ɣ usggas n 1992. 

Hâssan Id basàid izdar ad ismun ngr amarg amaziɣ azayku d umaziɣ atrar ifaɣ yat tadla n imurig s yat tɣarast srs izîlin. Ismun ngr imassn imadelann d imassn n [[Imaziɣn]] lli nttafa dar rways d trubba n ihwacn.

==Tasffift tamğarut==
Tasffift nes iğuran Ccahwa (2006) tis krâd d mrawtt gh tkafut n Idbasàid tga tagrawla mqqurn gh imasn ula ɣ uzawan, gh iwaliwn, ula ɣ usgiddi, tga yan usatur islkamn s idlsenn d izawann n wiyyâd, ismd gis Ḥasan id basɛid i uzawan amaziɣ amrruki yat tarmi tamaynut. 
